{
  "stem": "6258.1",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "They were, of course, always at noontime with us and into evening when they did not go somewhere else.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "But we were playing.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "I had-- So the house was full of my brother's colleagues.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "They were Jewish, and they were Polish.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And nobody made big deal out of it, well-- I had also many Polish friends, and we were playing.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "I was playing with dolls quite late.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "Not like-- I was over 10 years old, and I still have at least six dolls.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "But I didn't play like a little girl.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "I was telling them stories, which I promised myself to write, because I knew that I am going to be a writer.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "So this is how I play.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And then they were the friends of my brother, who suddenly took all my dolls and hang them on the chandeliers in the dining room.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And I hated this, and throw them out.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "But, anyway, we were going for-- for walk.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "We were playing sport.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "We were going skating and-- and going for ballet dances.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "Every girl-- I was-- since I was six, I was playing piano.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And-- and so it was a quiet life.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "I knew-- I knew what is expected from me, and there was no reason to revolt.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And maybe almost everyone was like this.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "We hardly-- well, first of all, I hardly become a teenager in a normal time.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "But it was not this kind of a revolt, rejecting everything and everyone, like it is here, I'm sorry to say.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "So it was a quiet, warm, very, very cordial life.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, we belong, of course, we belong-- I cannot even say whether we belong or not because I don't know this.",
      "word_count": 21
    }
  ],
